---
description: Generate or refresh a testify mock for one interface; --all walks every interface; --check is a CI drift gate.
allowed-tools: Bash(gofasta g*)
argument-hint: <InterfaceName> | --all | --check
---

Run `gofasta g mock $ARGUMENTS --json`. If `--check` reports
`MOCK_DRIFT`, the user has updated an interface but not regenerated
the mock — re-run without `--check` to refresh. If `--all`, report
the number of mocks refreshed.
